{"tid":884263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魔鬼身材！可愛女僕一個動作 讓網友都崩潰","createTime":"2018-10-31T12:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T13:02:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"759a90d440e4615ec5f1bc1580130e301dfb47b2","tid":884263,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"魔鬼身材常常被人用來誇讚女性身材傲人，不過近日日本也有名女性才木玲佳被人狂誇是「魔鬼」身材，原因除了她有個天使臉蛋外，還有個肌肉發達的身體，二頭肌甚至<br />\n比不少男生還大，引發討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/203657_f914b5aa2888a7366c4744061ed3d04b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F203657_f914b5aa2888a7366c4744061ed3d04b.png&h=eeacf63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據了解，才木玲佳在22歲時報名成為日本職業摔角聯盟「WRESTLE-1」的啦啦隊員，身高只有150公分的她在團體裡面並不顯眼，但後來有人發現她其實有個比男人還精壯的身材因此爆紅，甚至還成為了女子格鬥選手。後來才木玲佳更受邀上了不少日本綜藝節目，還曾打扮成女僕替知名漫畫宣傳。<br />\n <br />\n影片中可以看到，才木玲佳穿上女僕裝相當可愛，但下秒卻秀出健壯肌肉，開始做起料裡，過程中還不時利用空檔運動健身，「魔鬼身材」讓不少網友都目瞪口呆。"},{"pid":"38b1d504c889931b94ab98ad8e4b47927dffdeeb","tid":884263,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"嘔心"},{"pid":"86a3b34edc335886d6ba471a29894d3538ee558e","tid":884263,"uid":99700,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/yide168/1476969246-4029281871_n.png?v=1476969293\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fyide168%2F1476969246-4029281871_n.png%3Fv%3D1476969293&h=6de9abc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7995688025663d754165beadd6ffd7fa9a46f2a6","tid":884263,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"bbbfd1de0238dd81a60c9cf17a01967028a2bb68","tid":884263,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"似key上去"},{"pid":"e7aa0746effd1ca6fe2ce292b036f46db59b7af7","tid":884263,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RKHf_LnQssU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRKHf_LnQssU&d=WQC8%2FhqKkWRDHSgIYRUr2xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=181573a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RKHf_LnQssU</a>"},{"pid":"d6af0943d365134cbb8d6c1911f89dbbcbc2ce42","tid":884263,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}